title: Hour 2 - Charley Casserly (04-01-20)
itunes:title: Hour 2 - Charley Casserly (04-01-20)
description:
Doug Gottlieb and Chris Broussard fill in for Dan Patrick and predict what they think the NBA will look like when it eventually returns. Former NFL GM Charley Casserly jumps on to preview the NFL Draft and the guys discuss the best college basketball players of all time.
